4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" that prepares students for a career in data science and machine learning. The course is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge and can be completed in 16 weeks. Students will learn Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics, and will become proficient in using industry-standard tools.

The instructors for this course include Sayyed Nezhadi, a PhD in Artificial Intelligence with 25+ years of experience; Francesco Pugliese, a Computer Scientist and PhD in Robotics & Artificial Intelligence with deep expertise in deep learning and neural networks; and Manuel Mena, a Senior Data Scientist with experience in machine learning and business intelligence.

The course covers topics such as creating predictive models, working with supervised and unsupervised learning models, and developing AI projects. Students will also have the opportunity to practice solving real-life cases and learn how to ensure privacy and security in their AI projects.

The course duration is 16 weeks with 3 classes per week, and the maximum class size is 12 people. Upon completion, students will receive a certificate recognized by multiple organizations.

